NAME
    Template::Plugin::SumOf - calculate the sum with VMETHODS.

SYNOPSIS
        # in your script
        use Template;
        use Template::Plugin::SumOf;
        my $tt = Template->new;
        $tt->process(
            'template.html',
            {
                ary => [
                    { date => '2006-09-13', price => 300 },
                    { date => '2006-09-14', price => 500 }
                ]
            }
          )
          or die $tt->error;

        # in your template.
        [% USE SumOf -%]
        [%- FOR elem IN objects -%]
        [% elem.date  %],[% elem.price %]
        [% END -%]
        ,[% objects.sum_of('price') %]

        # result.
        2006-09-13,300
        2006-09-14,500
        ,800

DESCRIPTION
    You can easy to calculate sum of array, with VMETHODS.

BUGS AND LIMITATIONS
    No bugs have been reported.

    Please report any bugs or feature requests to
    "bug-template-plugin-sumof@rt.cpan.org", or through the web interface at
    <http://rt.cpan.org>.

